In this difficult time of crisis ..
The *"Iskcon India youth council"* is going to organize a free webinar on
the topic *"Business Yoga From Bhagvad Geeta" * by *Dr. Vivek Bindra ,
(Founder &CEO -BadaBusiness.com)* at online platform ...

*What the webinar is all about?*
-Learning success wisdom from Bhagvad Geeta.
-Overcoming three miseries of life.
Key Learning from the webinar -
-How to convert failures into life changing opportunities
-Improving focus and concentration power.
-Goal setting with success

*Who is Dr. Vivek Bindra?*

-International Motivational speaker,LEADERHIP consultant, BUSINESSES COACH
-5 times Guiness World Record Holder
-Best CEO coach in India by TIMES OF INDIA

somebody older compared to me, I reckon that older gents are

anything to hide. As soon as you reply i will send you my pictures.

Looking to collect an email from you soon). Your Foreign Alex Dahsa.

Alex Dasha
